headline: CHEEZ-IT® SNAP'D® TEAMS UP WITH REALITY TV ROYALTY PHAEDRA PARKS TO DROP THIS SEASON'S HOTTEST SNACK-INSPIRED ACCESSORY
summary: Prepare to dial up your snack and style game with a partnership that's serving looks and flavor. Cheez-It® Snap'd®—the chip baked with 100% real cheese and known for its crispy bite–is teaming up with reality TV icon and queen of snap backs, Phaedra Parks, to unveil the Cheez-It Snap'd Back Bag. Designed for fans who live for drama and demand a snack that matches their energy, this limited-edition snack-inspired accessory is made to dial up the drama and satisfy cravings, on screen and off.
